   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "# Wan 2.1 Text-to-Video Production\n",
    "Setup ComfyUI no Google Colab com Wan 2.1 para geração de vídeos"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 1. Instalação do ComfyUI e dependências"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "import subprocess, sys, os, threading, time, socket, urllib.request, json, warnings\n",
    "from IPython.display import clear_output, display, HTML\n",
    "warnings.filterwarnings('ignore')\n",
    "\n",
    "%cd /content\n",
    "print(\"-= Initial setup ComfyUI =-\")\n",
    "!git clone https://github.com/comfyanonymous/ComfyUI.git\n",
    "%cd ComfyUI\n",
    "!git pull\n",
    "\n",
    "print(\"-= Install dependencies =-\")\n",
    "!pip install -q torch torchvision torchaudio --index-url https://download.pytorch.org/whl/cu121\n",
    "!pip install -q -r requirements.txt\n",
    "!pip install -q av  # para suporte a vídeo"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 2. Instalar custom nodes para Wan 2.1"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "print(\"-= Installing Wan 2.1 custom nodes =-\")\n",
    "%cd /content/ComfyUI/custom_nodes\n",
    "\n",
    "# ComfyUI-Wan\n",
    "!git clone https://github.com/kijai/ComfyUI-Wan.git 2>/dev/null || echo \"Wan already cloned\"\n",
    "\n",
    "# Restart kernel message\n",
    "print(\"\\n✓ Custom nodes instalados. Continue para baixar modelos.\")"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 3. Baixar modelos Wan 2.1 (1.3B - recomendado para Colab)\n",
    "Model sizes:\n",
    "- 1.3B: ~2.5GB (funciona bem na T4/L4)\n",
    "- 14B: ~14GB (pode OOM na T4, usa L4/A100)"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "%cd /content/ComfyUI\n",
    "\n",
    "# Criar diretórios\n",
    "os.makedirs('models/unet', exist_ok=True)\n",
    "os.makedirs('models/vae', exist_ok=True)\n",
    "os.makedirs('models/clip', exist_ok=True)\n",
    "\n",
    "print(\"-= Downloading Wan 2.1 T2V 1.3B model =-\")\n",
    "!wget -q https://huggingface.co/Comfy-Org/Wan_2.1_T2V_1_3B-BP/resolve/main/split_files/diffusion_models/wan2.1_t2v_1.3B_bf16.safetensors -O models/unet/wan2.1_t2v_1.3B_bf16.safetensors\n",
    "\n",
    "print(\"-= Downloading VAE =-\")\n",
    "!wget -q https://huggingface.co/Comfy-Org/Wan_2.1_T2V_1_3B-BP/resolve/main/split_files/vae/wan_2.1_vae.safetensors -O models/vae/wan_2.1_vae.safetensors\n",
    "\n",
    "print(\"-= Downloading CLIP (umt5) =-\")\n",
    "!wget -q https://huggingface.co/Comfy-Org/Wan_2.1_T2V_1_3B-BP/resolve/main/split_files/text_encoders/umt5_xxl_fp8_e4m3fn_scaled.safetensors -O models/clip/umt5_xxl_fp8_e4m3fn_scaled.safetensors\n",
    "\n",
    "print(\"✓ Modelos baixados!\")"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 4. Iniciar ComfyUI"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "%cd /content/ComfyUI\n",
    "\n",
    "defiframe = '<iframe src="http://127.0.0.1:8188" width="100%" height="640px"></iframe>'\n",
    "\n",
    "def run_comfyui():\n",
    "    import subprocess\n",
    "    subprocess.run(['python', 'main.py', '--listen', '0.0.0.0', '--port', '8188'])\n",
    "\n",
    "thread = threading.Thread(target=run_comfyui, daemon=True)\n",
    "thread.start()\n",
    "time.sleep(10)\n",
    "\n",
    "print(\"ComfyUI starting...\")\n",
    "display(HTML('<a href=\"/proxy/8188\" target=\"_blank\">Abrir ComfyUI</a>'))"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 5. Workflow JSON\n",
    "Importe este workflow no ComfyUI:"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "workflow = {\n",
    "    \"last_node_id\": 47,\n",
